{"type":null,"faqId":20960,"title":"WLAN待机的时候会自动断开，怎么解决，手机默认是什么设置？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>这个问题是休眠策略的问题。进入的方法：在主屏幕，设置 &gt; 无线和网络 &gt; WLAN，再点击菜单键并进入高级 &gt; 在休眠状态下保持WLAN连接，设置为“始终”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>注：手机默认设置是始终，也就是一直可以正常连接。如果调整休眠策略就会使得在待机时自动断开。3个选项的含义如下：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>始终：一直保持WLAN的连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>仅限充电时：只有在充电时才一直保持连接，如果不充电，待机后3分钟断开连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>从不（会增加数据网络流量）：待机后3分钟断开连接。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4623","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1426837628000,"seriesProductName":"Pine-CL00,Pine-CL10,Pine-TL00M,Pine-TL10,Pine-TL20,Pine-UL00","visitedTimes":78,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}